,"","Post-training","Post-training optimization and model alignment","_ai/post-training.md",{"type":183,"children":184,"toc":387},"root",[185,194,201,207,238,244,249,276,282,287,314,320,325,336,342,347,365,371,376],{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":190},"element","h1",{"id":189},"后训练-post-training",[191],{"type":192,"value":193},"text","后训练 (Post-Training)",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":196,"children":198},"h2",{"id":197},"dpo直接偏好优化的对齐革命",[199],{"type":192,"value":200},"DPO：直接偏好优化的对齐革命",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":203,"children":204},"p",{},[205],{"type":192,"value":206},"DPO（Direct Preference Optimization）将 RLHF 的两阶段流程（训练 Reward Model + PPO 优化）压缩为单阶段。它直接在偏好数据上优化策略，数学上等价于带 KL 约束的 RL，但实现更简单、训练更稳定。无需强化学习，只需监督学习即可完成对齐，大大降低了后训练门槛。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":208,"children":209},{},[210,212,221,223,230,231],{"type":192,"value":211},"见：",{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":214,"children":218},"a",{"href":215,"rel":216},"https://arxiv.org/abs/2305.18290",[217],"nofollow",[219],{"type":192,"value":220},"DPO 论文",{"type":192,"value":222}," | ",{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":224,"children":227},{"href":225,"rel":226},"https://cameronrwolfe.substack.com/p/direct-preference-optimization",[217],[228],{"type":192,"value":229},"DPO 详解 - Deep Learning Focus",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":232,"children":235},{"href":233,"rel":234},"https://www.philschmid.de/rl-with-llms-in-2025-dpo",[217],[236],{"type":192,"value":237},"2025 DPO 对齐指南",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":239,"children":241},{"id":240},"grpodeepseek-r1-的推理突破关键",[242],{"type":192,"value":243},"GRPO：DeepSeek-R1 的推理突破关键",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":245,"children":246},{},[247],{"type":192,"value":248},"GRPO（Group Relative Policy Optimization）是 DeepSeek-R1 实现 reasoning 能力突破的核心技术。与传统 PPO 需要独立的 Critic 模型不同，GRPO 通过组内采样估计 baseline——对同一问题生成多组回答，以组内得分的相对排名作为优势估计，显存开销降低 50%，让超长思维链（Chain-of-Thought）的训练成为可能。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":250,"children":251},{},[252,253,260,261,268,269],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":254,"children":257},{"href":255,"rel":256},"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2501.12948",[217],[258],{"type":192,"value":259},"DeepSeek-R1 技术报告",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":262,"children":265},{"href":263,"rel":264},"https://medium.com/@sahin.samia/the-math-behind-deepseek-a-deep-dive-into-group-relative-policy-optimization-grpo-8a75007491ba",[217],[266],{"type":192,"value":267},"GRPO 数学原理",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":270,"children":273},{"href":271,"rel":272},"https://unsloth.ai/blog/r1-reasoning",[217],[274],{"type":192,"value":275},"Unsloth GRPO 本地训练",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":277,"children":279},{"id":278},"orposft-与对齐的合并",[280],{"type":192,"value":281},"ORPO：SFT 与对齐的合并",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":283,"children":284},{},[285],{"type":192,"value":286},"ORPO（Odds Ratio Preference Optimization）将传统两阶段流程（先 SFT 再 DPO）合并为单阶段。它用一个损失函数同时优化指令跟随和偏好对齐，训练效率提升一倍，且无需参考模型。这是目前最高效的后训练方法之一。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":288,"children":289},{},[290,291,298,299,306,307],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":292,"children":295},{"href":293,"rel":294},"https://arxiv.org/abs/2403.07691",[217],[296],{"type":192,"value":297},"ORPO 论文",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":300,"children":303},{"href":301,"rel":302},"https://huggingface.co/docs/trl/en/orpo_trainer",[217],[304],{"type":192,"value":305},"Hugging Face ORPO Trainer",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":308,"children":311},{"href":309,"rel":310},"https://www.analyticsvidhya.com/blog/2024/05/finetuning-llama-3-with-odds-ratio-preference-optimization/",[217],[312],{"type":192,"value":313},"Llama 3 ORPO 微调",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":315,"children":317},{"id":316},"simpo更简单直接的偏好优化",[318],{"type":192,"value":319},"SimPO：更简单直接的偏好优化",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":321,"children":322},{},[323],{"type":192,"value":324},"SimPO 进一步简化 DPO，移除参考模型，直接优化响应间的胜率。它引入\"长度归一化\"，避免模型生成冗长但空洞的回复，是对 DPO 的实用改进。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":326,"children":327},{},[328,329],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":330,"children":333},{"href":331,"rel":332},"https://huggingface.co/docs/trl/en/index",[217],[334],{"type":192,"value":335},"SimPO 介绍",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":337,"children":339},{"id":338},"trl后训练的一站式解决方案",[340],{"type":192,"value":341},"TRL：后训练的一站式解决方案",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":343,"children":344},{},[345],{"type":192,"value":346},"TRL（Transformer Reinforcement Learning）是 Hugging Face 生态中的后训练全栈库，集成 SFT、DPO、PPO、GRPO、Reward Modeling 等方法。它与 transformers、peft、datasets 无缝协作，是入门后训练的首选工具。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":348,"children":349},{},[350,351,358,359],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":352,"children":355},{"href":353,"rel":354},"https://github.com/huggingface/trl",[217],[356],{"type":192,"value":357},"TRL GitHub",{"type":192,"value":222},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":360,"children":362},{"href":331,"rel":361},[217],[363],{"type":192,"value":364},"TRL 文档",{"type":186,"tag":195,"props":366,"children":368},{"id":367},"后训练最佳实践数据质量-数量",[369],{"type":192,"value":370},"后训练最佳实践：数据质量 > 数量",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":372,"children":373},{},[374],{"type":192,"value":375},"偏好对的质量远胜于数量——1000 条精心标注的偏好对 > 10000 条噪声数据。推荐流程：冷启动（高质量 SFT 建立基础指令跟随能力）→ 多轮对齐（SFT → DPO → RL，逐步逼近目标分布）→ 能力保持（定期在基础能力测试集上评估，防止对齐税）。",{"type":186,"tag":202,"props":377,"children":378},{},[379,380],{"type":192,"value":211},{"type":186,"tag":213,"props":381,"children":384},{"href":382,"rel":383},"https://www.53ai.com/news/finetuning/2026010417029.html",[217],[385],{"type":192,"value":386},"LLM 微调全指南",{"title":178,"searchDepth":388,"depth":388,"links":389},2,[390,391,392,393,394,395],{"id":197,"depth":388,"text":200},{"id":240,"depth":388,"text":243},{"id":278,"depth":388,"text":281},{"id":316,"depth":388,"text":319},{"id":338,"depth":388,"text":341},{"id":367,"depth":388,"text":370},"markdown","content:6.maps:_ai:training:post-training.md","content","6.maps/_ai/training/post-training.md","6.maps/_ai/training/post-training","md",[403,407],{"_path":404,"title":405,"description":406},"/maps/_ai/training/fine-tuning","Fine-tuning","Model fine-tuning techniques and best practices",{"_path":408,"title":409,"description":410},"/maps/_ai/training/topology-aware-scheduling","拓扑感知调度","拓扑感知调度是一种在分布式计算环境中，根据硬件拓扑结构和网络性能来优化任务调度和资源分配的方法，以提高整体系统的效率和性能。",1772504960817]